      • filterValue

        public static String filterValue​(String value,
                                 String matchedString,
                                 String stringMatchOperatorName)
        Filter the value based on the stringMatchOperatorName and the provided string by returning the original value if it matches, or null otherwise.The available match operators are:
        • EQUALS
        • NOT_EQUALS
        • CONTAINS
        • NOT_CONTAINS
        • STARTS_WITH
        • NOT_STARTS_WITH
        • ENDS_WITH
        • NOT_ENDS_WITH
        • IS_BLANK
        • IS_NOT_BLANK
        • MATCHES_REGEX
        • NOT_MATCHES_REGEX
        Parameters:
        value - the value to filter
        matchedString - the string to match (nullable and irrelevant for operators IS_BLANK and IS_NOT_BLANK)
        stringMatchOperatorName - the name of the match operator
        Returns:
        the original value if it matches, or null otherwise

      • filterValues

        public static List<String> filterValues​(List<String> values,
                                        String matchedString,
                                        String stringMatchOperatorName,
                                        boolean removeDuplicates)
        Filter the values based on the stringMatchOperatorName and the provided string to match. Returns the list of matched values, or null if none matched. The available match operators are:
        • EQUALS
        • NOT_EQUALS
        • CONTAINS
        • NOT_CONTAINS
        • STARTS_WITH
        • NOT_STARTS_WITH
        • ENDS_WITH
        • NOT_ENDS_WITH
        • IS_BLANK
        • IS_NOT_BLANK
        • MATCHES_REGEX
        • NOT_MATCHES_REGEX
        Parameters:
        values - the list of values to filter
        matchedString - the string to match (nullable and irrelevant for operators IS_BLANK and IS_NOT_BLANK)
        stringMatchOperatorName - the name of the match operator
        removeDuplicates - toggle to remove duplicates or not
        Returns:
        the list of matched values, or null if none matched
